org.apache.flex.abc.visitors

Interface ITraitsVisitor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IVisitor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DelegatingTraitsVisitor, NilTraitsVisitor, ScopedDefinitionTraitsVisitor

    public interface ITraitsVisitor
extends IVisitor
    An ITraitsVisitor defines the individual trait entries of a traits collection.
